item.title: Worst Miss EVER!! Lorenzo Insigne (Pescara) v Gubbio (April 29th, 2012)
item.description:
Worst Miss EVER!! Lorenzo Insigne (Pescara) v Gubbio (April 29th, 2012)
Sunday, April 29th, 2012 Lorenzo Insigne (Pescara) produces worst miss ever contender v GubbioBefore Lorenzo Insigne hits global infamy for one of the most impossible misses you will ever see, it is important to point out that the diminutive forward is one of Italy's brightest talents. Insigne, nicknamed in some quarters as "The Messi of the Adriatic," is currently on loan at Pescara from Napoli and has banged in the goals, with his current count at 14 in 31 appearances. His talents have also been noticed at Under-21 level where he has claimed three goals in four games for Italy's Azzurrini. But, Insigne's miss on Saturday in the first half of Pescara's 2-0 win at Gubbio was truly horrific and since he was standing on the goal line, is simply inexplicable. So bad is the miss that it isn't even fair to call it "a miss of the season contender," it is a lot worse than that!

Siaran Astro didapati lebih kurang 5 minit kelewatan, jadi itu, mereka mempunyai masa untuk menapis berita yang tidak baik untuk Kerajaan Malaysia (BN) dan menyembunyikan apa yang mereka mahu menyembunyikan. 在左边，BBC的新闻播放时间是晚上10点（马来西亚时间）于2012年4月28日。 右边的是大马Astro播出的。他们播放时间延迟了约5分钟，让他们有时间来过滤大马政府如何对待人民的丑闻。

item.description:
IL PASTICCIO UDINESE 2-0 LAZIO
Finale turbolento al Friuli nella gara vinta dall'Udinese sulla Lazio per 2 a 0. Con i friulani avanti di un gol e con pochi secondi da giocare, parte un contropiede con il nuovo entrato Pereyra. Parte anche un fischio, probabilmente dalla tribuna, sicuramente non dell'arbitro: Gonzalez equivoca e molla la rincorsa al bianconero, Marchetti addirittura si getta a terra, Pereyra se ne frega e mette in rete a porta vuota. Ne segue una rissa che vede coinvolti i giocatori (espulso il laziale Dias) e i dirigenti
